  "purpose": "By January 2027, Citizens United Facts feels like an operating system for civic education \u2014 not a traditional website. Every account enters a personalized civic workspace. Platform remembers learning, interests, location, organizations, volunteer roles, and goals. Every role works from the same platform with different permissions.",
  "governing_principle": "The Arkansas Civic Operating System exists to make civic education personal. One institution. One login. One trusted platform. Thousands of individual journeys. Together building a stronger Arkansas through knowledge, volunteer service, community leadership, and lifelong civic learning.",
